        "description": "<p>WordPress 4.5 added the ability to login using the registered user&#8217;s email address in place of the username. When this plugin is active, the ability to login using the email address in place of the username is removed, and the label of the input field is changed to reflect this.<\/p>\n",
        "installation": "<ol>\n<li>Upload the plugin folder to the &#8216;\/wp-content\/plugins\/&#8217; directory<\/li>\n<li>Activate the plugin through the &#8216;Plugins&#8217; menu in WordPress<\/li>\n<\/ol>\n",
        "faq": "\n<dt id='what%20levels%20of%20support%20are%20available%3F'>\nWhat levels of support are available?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>You can receive free support for the plugin if you have problems getting it working. To access this please open a new topic on the <a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/support\/plugin\/no-login-by-email-address\/\" title=\"No login by email address plugin support forum\" rel=\"ugc\">plugin support forum<\/a> all communication must take place on the forum for free support.<\/p>\n<p>If you require a greater level of support than can be provided on the plugin support forum on WordPress.org &#8211; eg you prefer not to post the url, you can request non-free support via the <a href=\"https:\/\/cubecolour.co.uk\/premium-support\/\" title=\"paid email support form for cubecolour plugins\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">paid email support form for cubecolour plugins<\/a> form.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='where%20is%20the%20plugin%27s%20admin%20page%3F'>\nWhere is the plugin&#8217;s admin page?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>There isn&#8217;t one. This is a lightweight plugin with no options.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='are%20there%20any%20other%20free%20cubecolour%20plugins%3F'>\nAre there any other free cubecolour plugins?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>Yes, if you like this plugin, you may like some of my other plugins in the WordPress.org plugins directory. You can see these listed on my <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/numeeja\/\" title=\"cubecolour profile\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">profile<\/a> page under the &#8216;plugins&#8217; tab.<\/p>\n<\/p>\n<dt id='i%20am%20using%20the%20plugin%20and%20i%20love%20it%2C%20how%20can%20i%20show%20my%20appreciation%3F'>\nI am using the plugin and I love it, how can I show my appreciation?\n<\/h4>\n<p>\n<p>You can donate any amount via <a href=\"https:\/\/cubecolour.co.uk\/wp\/\" title=\"cubecolour donation page\" rel=\"nofollow ugc\">my donation page<\/a>.<\/p>\n<p>If you find No login by email address useful, I would also appreciate a review on the <a href=\"https:\/\/wordpress.org\/support\/view\/plugin-reviews\/no-login-by-email-address\/\" title=\"No login by email address plugin reviews\" rel=\"ugc\">plugin review page<\/a><\/p>\n<\/p>\n\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.3.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Support for WooCommerce added<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.2.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>WP 4.7+ updates the default input label from &#8216;Username or Email&#8217; to &#8216;Username or Email Address&#8217; so this new string is now replaced.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.1.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>New filter to remove reference to email address from the Username field label for login forms added using wp_login_form<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h4>1.0.0<\/h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Initial Version<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n",
        "screenshots": "<ol><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/no-login-by-email-address\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=1485163\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/no-login-by-email-address\/assets\/screenshot-1.png?rev=1485163\" alt=\"The login screen without this plugin installed\"><\/a><p>The login screen without this plugin installed<\/p><\/li><li><a href=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/no-login-by-email-address\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=1485163\"><img src=\"https:\/\/ps.w.org\/no-login-by-email-address\/assets\/screenshot-2.png?rev=1485163\" alt=\"The login screen with this plugin installed\"><\/a><p>The login screen with this plugin installed<\/p><\/li><\/ol>",
        "reviews": "<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Excellenteetoe!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/jjnw\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/7f69d47ae20a464059aa0230d49f11d5?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/7f69d47ae20a464059aa0230d49f11d5?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/jjnw\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">JJNW<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 7, 2021<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Very cool, very awesome! Very easy, very simple. Can't use email to login - LOVE IT!!!!!<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">Do the job!<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/oupla\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/473bb11052bd2fce899224cc632bbe7b?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/473bb11052bd2fce899224cc632bbe7b?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/oupla\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">oupla<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">July 6, 2019<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Really fantastic! \nThis plugin did work for wordpress but not for WooCommerce. I contacted the author to know if it was possible to support WooCommerce too. he done!\nThank you so much, this plugin remove some confusion for WooCommerce customers when they try to login with their email with error warning.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">no login by email - just what i wanted<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/wpwalker\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/587143661507589409fec4542fe91bbf?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/587143661507589409fec4542fe91bbf?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/wpwalker\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">wpwalker<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">December 31, 2016<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\">Thanks for this! exactly what i was looking for. works with no problem.<\/div>\n<\/div>\n<div class=\"review\">\n\t<div class=\"review-head\">\n\t\t<div class=\"reviewer-info\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"review-title-section\">\n\t\t\t\t<h4 class=\"review-title\">More security - solved easy<\/h4>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"star-rating\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"wporg-ratings\" aria-label=\"5 out of 5 stars\" data-title-template=\"%s out of 5 stars\" data-rating=\"5\" style=\"color:#ffb900;\"><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><span class=\"star dashicons dashicons-star-filled\"><\/span><\/div>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t<p class=\"reviewer\">\n\t\t\t\tBy <a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tidros\/\"><img alt='' src='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/7cc521373ea4cb5006b0cc36c94635eb?s=16&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g' srcset='https:\/\/secure.gravatar.com\/avatar\/7cc521373ea4cb5006b0cc36c94635eb?s=32&#038;d=monsterid&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-16 photo' height='16' width='16' loading='lazy' decoding='async'\/><\/a><a href=\"https:\/\/profiles.wordpress.org\/tidros\/\" class=\"reviewer-name\">tidros<\/a> on <span class=\"review-date\">September 3, 2016<\/span>\t\t\t<\/p>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t<\/div>\n\t<div class=\"review-body\"><p>Thanks to the developer for this useful and easy to use plugin!<br \/>\nFor security reasons was it for me important to remove the ability to login using the email address in place of the username, and this plugin solved this in only one step (just install it and forget it). It works fine on WP 4.5.3 and runs without any conflict beside 18 other plugins.\n<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<\/div>\n"
